    "On each ON value the current KNX state is read and the inverse is sent. Use for buttons that should toggle a KNX light on/off.": {"en": "On each ON value the current KNX state is read and the inverse is sent. Use for buttons that should toggle a KNX light on/off.", "de": "Bei jedem EIN-Wert wird der aktuelle KNX-Zustand gelesen und invertiert gesendet. Für Taster, die ein KNX-Licht ein-/ausschalten sollen.", "ru": "При каждом значении ВКЛ текущее состояние KNX считывается и отправляется инвертированное. Для кнопок, которые должны переключать свет KNX.", "pt": "On each ON value the current KNX state is read and the inverse is sent. Use for buttons that should toggle a KNX light on/off.", "nl": "On each ON value the current KNX state is read and the inverse is sent. Use for buttons that should toggle a KNX light on/off.", "fr": "On each ON value the current KNX state is read and the inverse is sent. Use for buttons that should toggle a KNX light on/off.", "it": "On each ON value the current KNX state is read and the inverse is sent. Use for buttons that should toggle a KNX light on/off.", "es": "On each ON value the current KNX state is read and the inverse is sent. Use for buttons that should toggle a KNX light on/off.", "pl": "On each ON value the current KNX state is read and the inverse is sent. Use for buttons that should toggle a KNX light on/off.", "uk": "On each ON value the current KNX state is read and the inverse is sent. Use for buttons that should toggle a KNX light on/off.", "zh-cn": "On each ON value the current KNX state is read and the inverse is sent. Use for buttons that should toggle a KNX light on/off."},
    "Only ON values are forwarded, OFF is ignored. Use for scene triggers or door openers where the source sends ON/OFF (press/release).": {"en": "Only ON values are forwarded, OFF is ignored. Use for scene triggers or door openers where the source sends ON/OFF (press/release).", "de": "Nur EIN-Werte werden weitergeleitet, AUS wird ignoriert. Für Szenenauslöser oder Türöffner bei denen die Quelle EIN/AUS (Drücken/Loslassen) sendet.", "ru": "Только значения ВКЛ передаются, ВЫКЛ игнорируется. Для триггеров сцен или открывателей дверей, где источник отправляет ВКЛ/ВЫКЛ (нажать/отпустить).", "pt": "Only ON values are forwarded, OFF is ignored. Use for scene triggers or door openers where the source sends ON/OFF (press/release).", "nl": "Only ON values are forwarded, OFF is ignored. Use for scene triggers or door openers where the source sends ON/OFF (press/release).", "fr": "Only ON values are forwarded, OFF is ignored. Use for scene triggers or door openers where the source sends ON/OFF (press/release).", "it": "Only ON values are forwarded, OFF is ignored. Use for scene triggers or door openers where the source sends ON/OFF (press/release).", "es": "Only ON values are forwarded, OFF is ignored. Use for scene triggers or door openers where the source sends ON/OFF (press/release).", "pl": "Only ON values are forwarded, OFF is ignored. Use for scene triggers or door openers where the source sends ON/OFF (press/release).", "uk": "Only ON values are forwarded, OFF is ignored. Use for scene triggers or door openers where the source sends ON/OFF (press/release).", "zh-cn": "Only ON values are forwarded, OFF is ignored. Use for scene triggers or door openers where the source sends ON/OFF (press/release)."},
